msgid "7. Vos droits"
msgstr "7. Your rights"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Accéder"
msgstr "Access"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "à vos renseignements"
msgstr "your information"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Rectifier"
msgstr "Rectify"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "des informations inexactes"
msgstr "inaccurate information"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Retirer votre consentement"
msgstr "Withdraw your consent"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "en tout temps"
msgstr "at any time"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Demander la cessation de diffusion"
msgstr "Request cessation of distribution"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "de photos"
msgstr "of photos"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Demander la portabilité"
msgstr "Request portability"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "de vos données"
msgstr "of your data"

#: page-confidentialite.php:334
msgid "Délai de réponse : 30 jours."
msgstr "Response time: 30 days."

#: page-confidentialite.php:335
msgid "8. Témoins (cookies)"
msgstr "8. Cookies"

#: page-confidentialite.php:335
msgid ""
"Témoins essentiels activés par défaut. Témoins analytiques activés "
"uniquement après consentement explicite via la bannière de consentement."
msgstr ""
"Essential cookies enabled by default. Analytical cookies enabled only after "
"explicit consent via the consent banner."

#: page-confidentialite.php:336
msgid "9. Sécurité"
msgstr "9. Security"

#: page-confidentialite.php:336
msgid ""
"Connexion HTTPS, mots de passe forts, mises à jour régulières, accès limité "
"aux personnes autorisées."
msgstr ""
"HTTPS connection, strong passwords, regular updates, access limited to "
"authorized persons."

#: page-confidentialite.php:337
msgid "10. Incident de confidentialité"
msgstr "10. Privacy incident"

#: page-confidentialite.php:337
msgid ""
"En cas d'incident présentant un risque sérieux, notification à la CAI et aux "
"personnes concernées dans les meilleurs délais."
msgstr ""
"In case of an incident presenting a serious risk, notification to the CAI "
"and affected persons as soon as possible."

